  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8251fb24-dbff-45bf-93c2-a56ba2e6d038\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-11a188fb-173f-4bc6-b83e-f9e1677eac74\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8a589f2c-3563-409c-80b0-fcdac57e2e55\">안녕하세요, </span><span style=\"background-color:#ffef34;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-694ca6f8-1acb-411f-aa66-7f88614a1bf4\">이수한의원</span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-15cf5558-bb07-42a5-8c5e-38b2ba263ca6\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-8251fb24-dbff-45bf-93c2-a56ba2e6d038\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0bb0dd4f-14c7-452c-a306-eb0072a2b3f9\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"9\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_9.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-88c60993-041d-44c1-8134-ac4758c5cd4b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fcbfcf48-2cb7-462a-9b17-000f88ed728f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0cb97867-ed5f-4fe5-bc24-354d54f0ecec\"><b>무더운 여름, 건강 관리가 더 어려워지죠?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bc8f2f13-30b9-4ec1-af6e-495107f43952\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-241bb013-c939-409a-8a9e-aa6cab467247\">더위로 인해 몸은 쉽게 지치고, 수면의 질도 떨어지며, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-df485d1c-baee-4113-8a46-5abfdfe95e46\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-90d5bf61-8ec4-40c7-8c95-f2df978afb6b\">식사마저 소홀해지기 쉽습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-61781ff5-b408-448b-b87c-bed17415e28b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5748eb32-307d-4bdd-a15c-abb2ce1fe44d\">여름철에는 작은 습관 관리가 건강을 지키는 핵심입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-88c60993-041d-44c1-8134-ac4758c5cd4b\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-bd8f86a0-604c-47de-8dff-02a41f8cea2f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a06cff5c-5dec-4600-baf7-170e1a52a81e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-a06cff5c-5dec-4600-baf7-170e1a52a81e\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/384c5d8ddb0e9833.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"800\", \"originalHeight\" : \"800\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/384c5d8ddb0e9833.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/384c5d8ddb0e9833.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-a06cff5c-5dec-4600-baf7-170e1a52a81e\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-1ba77ee1-c23e-4317-95c8-3629287f2069\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a8b4d3b5-58c9-4ccb-a3ba-6dee1bac7d8b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-67f57899-b157-49bb-a4d4-189aaaf626c5\"><b>여름철 더위를 이기는 가벼운 운동 습관</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5e8a1fc6-0605-45e3-bce4-821043d8fdd2\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c166571a-bcde-49cc-aaca-bdaa7b77ce21\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3feb1509-59d0-4b76-a372-c1c0e1a9d09a\">무더운 낮 시간대보다는 기온이 내려간 저녁에 가볍게 땀을 흘려주는 운동이 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-128f80ce-ae54-41de-9f36-9db20b6bde6a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-64aca849-02ad-4700-ade2-4785993efeb0\">좋습니다. 과격한 운동보다는 가벼운 걷기나 스트레칭을 통해 순환을 돕고, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-27f8d3ed-f7a9-4758-9f4d-7d23943a0cfa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ebfee82a-d2b1-4cdd-8b74-31ca0e8b83ba\">숙면에도 도움을 줍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4e665b4b-5fa3-4f78-9f14-29e11c1425b0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-95abd4f5-cf22-40a9-ba7f-dc5daff347ac\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ec615e7b-d232-44e3-b4fa-b5ad925b5540\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7db22243-c145-4b40-9887-4d3fd8f1c0e2\"><b>시원하게 잠드는 숙면 비법</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b2d4b19d-6f18-4302-b800-4e208688b3f3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-11ed88dc-61e4-47d9-8cd8-8080aa42e980\">열대야에는 수면의 질이 크게 떨어집니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-936573de-4dbd-461a-a831-b9faacef61c9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1387f1f9-f609-4c96-bc77-1dc444495476\">메밀 베개나 죽부인을 사용하면 체온을 낮추는 데 도움이 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-23a4086c-8787-40c7-8627-621695a5066c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a6278797-b815-4245-b4c6-3fd8326ebfda\">시원한 환경을 유지하되 에어컨 바람을 직접 쐬지 않도록 주의해야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-04f32b3b-554a-4bf0-965b-2ddc06227b4a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4aa76bcb-af1f-420f-befc-6c0ecca2fae1\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bcbc4f25-bc24-4f40-82fe-3ceb759f1316\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dd337ccc-b58f-4b70-bdbd-4ec131386c68\"><b>여름철 보양식과 음식</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4d94da1f-2762-4ccc-bf60-c0edacd78605\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-201c50d9-04fe-4a00-bef3-d2fb319f5455\">땀으로 기운이 빠지기 쉬운 여름에는 제철 보양식으로 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3903f511-067f-4fb9-ac05-1a221d2e92b2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-65434c57-780a-4213-971d-9c345beefd52\">기력을 보충하는 것이 필요합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-be63f4f7-23ec-41f5-bea2-a021ab703619\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e7090eab-fbfb-423c-aaf4-4da221f09d94\">삼계탕, 장어, 오리 같은 대표적인 보양식뿐만 아니라 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a6ae8842-20c9-4bd9-a169-337830a96570\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3e4a2b92-66db-4989-bc3c-8df369b7163c\">수분과 미네랄이 풍부한 제철 과일과 채소를 함께 섭취하면 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8ae7e203-8784-4206-a330-07290aeb7b5c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-20064b78-0489-41d9-a2d2-bc7ec42cdec5\">체력 회복에 도움이 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-989a56c2-1b8c-4c9c-b9d4-c1975521dcbb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ac0029a2-f91f-415e-86f5-65e3035018c8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cc39ba0d-3971-4c2e-9326-daa1d8be0c4d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fc258090-ddc7-446f-a988-4836bd94e601\"><b>에어컨병과 더위병 관리</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cec3cc70-633e-457f-9d68-1b652b96c698\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4b95ec4f-e8f0-4232-a3e6-2f8cf12e916f\">여름철에는 냉방병(에어컨병)과 더위병이 흔히 나타납니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-202021ce-56f4-4f56-b378-96fc0906eab3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e33c89f7-37a0-4151-a456-064e4261a1ea\">에어컨에 오래 노출되면 두통, 소화불량, 몸살 증상 등이 생길 수 있고, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-068b8905-06ff-4add-bc93-c7c072422ffb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f2cd6e46-e34d-4e89-8e9a-a296e0e3f892\">반대로 더위에 오래 노출되면 열사병이나 탈수로 이어질 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-63416dc5-8dd6-452e-9466-17486ab59778\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-946488ee-f12a-4f61-a15c-103528d6eb72\">몸을 지나치게 덥히거나 식히지 않고, 적절한 온도 조절이 필요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-5e8a1fc6-0605-45e3-bce4-821043d8fdd2\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e753415c-5afe-4fe6-9e46-1fbb44e68589\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div cl